        <h3>15. Comprehensive Digital Marketing Agency ($2,000-$4,000/month)</h3>
        <p>Partner with agencies specializing in home services marketing. They handle Google Ads, SEO, social media, and website optimization. Expect 40-75% increase in qualified leads within 6 months when properly executed.</p>

        <h3>16. Television Advertising ($1,500-$3,500/month)</h3>
        <p>Local cable TV spots during home improvement shows, morning news, and weather segments. 30-second spots cost $200-$800 depending on time slots and market size. TV advertising builds brand authority and generates 15-30 monthly inquiries.</p>

        <h3>17. Trade Show and Home Show Participation ($800-$2,000 per event)</h3>
        <p>Exhibit at 6-10 local home shows annually. Booth costs range $800-$2,000 plus staffing expenses. Generate 50-150 leads per show with proper booth design and follow-up systems. Focus on spring and fall home improvement events.</p>

        <h3>18. Strategic Partnership Programs ($500-$1,500/month)</h3>
        <p>Partner with real estate agents, home inspectors, and general contractors for referral arrangements. Provide lunch-and-learns about HVAC systems. Well-structured partnerships generate 20-40 high-quality referrals annually.</p>

        <h3>19. Advanced CRM and Marketing Automation ($300-$800/month)</h3>
        <p>Implement systems like <a href="/hvac/pricing/servicetitan-pricing" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">ServiceTitan</a> or <a href="/hvac/pricing/housecall-pro-pricing" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Housecall Pro</a> with marketing automation features. Automatically nurture leads, schedule follow-ups, and track customer lifetime value. Advanced CRMs increase conversion rates 15-25%.</p>

        <h3>20. Outbound Sales and Lead Generation ($1,000-$3,000/month)</h3>
        <p>Hire dedicated sales staff to call homeowners in target demographics. Focus on homes with older HVAC systems for replacement opportunities. Professional outbound programs generate 25-50 qualified appointments monthly.</p>

        <h3>21. Comprehensive Local Sponsorships ($800-$2,500/month)</h3>
        <p>Sponsor little league teams, community events, and charity fundraisers. Include your logo on uniforms, banners, and event materials. Local sponsorships build community goodwill and generate 10-20 referrals annually.</p>
